  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_173",
    "english": "A monstrosity that looks like a fish. It appears both in the human world and the Demon Realm, disturbing the ecosystem, but its life or origins are still mysterious. Those who have adjusted to the cold waters of the Demon Realm's ocean shoot deep-freeze water to freeze their prey.",
